ygData.messageBody:
Hi Jorge =)) Currently Fosan is working the
Oasis. Soloing..but willing to group for deep water
goblin pets. Barely able to gain exp because I die a
lot..I'm considering hunting stuff in Skarana since the
overcrowding makes it hard to find targets in Oasis. Fosan
goes after low blues like DW Caimans and occasional
undead or an orc warriors. When Fosan gets a little
bigger the Evil Eyes spawn in Beholder's Maze better
start shaking muhahaha.<br>Hope this helps.
